  "desc": "Check with your PoC the latest process/tools.\n\nSonar uses Vanta for a lot of our security and compliance tasks. One of them is the repository of approved responses to common security, legal, and vendor-related questions. \n\nTo support scale and complexity of the asks, we are \"shifting left\" the access to this repository, including the SE team. You are intimately involved in customer engagements, and in the best position to support many of these asks.\n\nThe InfoSec Team will still be here to support you in the tool, and improvements, etc. \n\nThere are two primary tools -\n\n1. Vanta (SSO Tile) - this is for putting questionnaires directly into the tool and having it automatically provide answers.\n\n1. [Vanta AI Plug-in Brower Extension](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/vanta-questionnaire-autom/ncclamkmacaipikhipjillbckmpclakb \"‌\") - good for one off questions.\n\n‌\n\nCurrently (Jan 2026) we can use Vanta for RFI’s and Security Questionnaires.",
